### Test 1 — POST via JSON
POST https://localhost:5190/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Hobbit",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "genre": "Fantasy",
  "notes": "A comfort reread",
  "status": "Completed"
}

###

### Test 2 — POST via Form Data
POST https://localhost:5190/api/books/form
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

title=Neuromancer&author=William Gibson&genre=Sci-Fi&status=Want to Read

###

### Test 3 — POST via Query String
POST https://localhost:5190/api/books/query?title=1984&author=George Orwell&genre=Classic&status=Completed

###

### Test 4 — GET all books
GET https://localhost:5190/api/books

###

### Test 5 — GET with search, sort and pagination
GET https://localhost:5190/api/books?search=bran&sortBy=Title&sortDirection=asc&page=1&pageSize=5

